      <Version>1</Version>
      <Date>8/13/2015</Date>
      <Description>Deleted the LVM_2 CAL (Previously tied to CalID: _T03xMLrmEeSOH7Idfz1A2w), and re-added this CAL back in under the new CalID: _IRih8EIfEeW1KJbfjB0QJg to be able to associate this CAL now to the new enumeration CAL (LVM_X ) that's referenced in the updated GIS511_LVM.enumdef file in this release. </Description>
      <Author>Ginnard Kimbrough</Author>
